Typical Hong-Kong style dessert made with soya beans. Comes in hot or cold in various flavours. Amongst them i like ginger the best. Add a dash of those yellow sugar it's magic! Freshly made soya bean milk is also available.  You get also all kinds of friend bean curbs is all sort of styles. Quite a unique Hong-Kong dining experience.
Traditional, yummy and local tastes.

reviews.text: the people waiting for bus will look deep into your eyes when they stand right next to you while you're eating. if you enjoy being watched while eating, feel free to chill out here. You can be a super star

D 呀姐服務態度極差，以前都5係咁，越黎越衰，問佢加多匙炸蒜蓉都會比呀姐鬧，我1個人去食左碗都加多個餃子同可樂，$72蚊，食個lunch 72蚊冇問題，問題係想加多匙炸蒜蓉都5得個下嬲丫嘛😤
在此祝你生意興隆，我就5會再去幫襯嫁咁！
著撚晒呀！！
原因係收費太貴，本人唔會去！
價錢合理，味道不錯，但太擠迫，純粹填飽肚就要即走
最平最好味嘅就係11元1枝嘅豆漿小食最好味就係鹵水鸡中翼和豆卜。
